{"tid":1167044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實呢兩三年有仲有幾多香港人去德國申請庇護?","createTime":"2019-05-22T23:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T00:20:41.000Z","uid":41101,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71eb31ec151e0f074b34b797925967158c6df236","tid":1167044,"uid":41101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:11:04.000Z","msg":"綜合返唔同報導<br />\n黃台仰李東昇係2017年11月4日經台灣去德國柏林<br />\n其後2018年5月獲庇護<br />\n於是上返BAMF(移民及難民署)睇返德國政府難民申請統計 <br />\n<br />\n2017年7月已經有人申請 但冇接納 (可能係申請人自行撤回申請)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-juli-2017.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-juli-2017.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyowKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=cd1ffbb5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-juli-2017.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXJ3naF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXJ3naF.jpg&h=44e9295b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年11月有2單係首次庇護申請 應該係黃李二人<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2017.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2017.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyowKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=2386d62f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2017.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xq1AdpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXq1AdpG.jpg&h=b533d41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月有2個人根據難民法獲難民庇護 應該係黃李二人<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyowKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=0a1b85c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-mai-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWXr4yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWXr4yZ.jpg&h=fdfb46b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月又有1宗申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2018.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyowKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=979a5161\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-november-2018.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rxu92mR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxu92mR.jpg&h=4acb5731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年1月 如圖所見同2017年7月結果一樣 呢單應該係11月嗰份申請<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-januar-2019.pdf?__blob=publicationFile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bamf.de%2FSharedDocs%2FAnlagen%2FDE%2FDownloads%2FInfothek%2FStatistik%2FAsyl%2Fhkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-januar-2019.pdf%3F__blob%3DpublicationFile&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1UoyowKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=01c0de8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bamf.de/SharedDocs/Anlagen/DE/Downloads/Infothek/Statistik/Asyl/hkl-antrags-entscheidungs-bestandsstatistik-januar-2019.pdf?__blob=publicationFile</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCEJ6Px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCEJ6Px.jpg&h=4bbb425f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後一直至今就冇香港人嘅庇護申請 <br />\nBtw剩係搵到2017年4月起嘅統計<br />\n所以申請庇護嘅人可能比想像中多"},{"pid":"e7ec28e19861bb464e9017b02ae12833761968b3","tid":1167044,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:56:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會俾德國人當我哋同啲sandnigga一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97578efafb3bada3e7d69a991f8318a48214d0d9","tid":1167044,"uid":117786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:05:53.000Z","msg":"成個連登去哂"},{"pid":"7cb1cfd41462dab914ec0e2755e9d711ba105818","tid":1167044,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:20:41.000Z","msg":"睇到單新聞我係到諗，<br />\n黎緊反送中遊行，<br />\n會唔會有人唔夠錢投資移民法，<br />\n當日衝突政總，<br />\n比人拉就去德國申請政治難民(移民)<br />\n<br />\n利申: 學術討論，反對暴力"}]}